<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="disadvantage-n">disadvantage <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌdɪsəd'vɑːntɪdʒ/    美 /ˌdɪsəd'væntɪdʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>不利条件；劣势</strong></h4>
<p>反 advantage </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One <strong>major disadvantage of</strong> this area is the lack of public transport. 
这个地区的一大不利条件是缺少公共交通。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Every advantage has its disadvantage.
有利必有弊。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-a-disadvantage">at a disadvantage</h3>
<p>1.<strong>处于不利地位：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I feel rather at a disadvantage talking to her because she’s so clever. 
她太伶俐，我跟她讲话总觉得吃亏。</p></div></div>